content: This is the Gyeongui Line Forest Road connecting Hongdae Station. There are pretty shops lined up along the landscaping in the middle, so it's great for a date at a restaurant and a walk in the cool breeze.
It is regrettable that it is shorter and less distinctive than a typical downtown walking course or Hongdae course with a quiet and unsteady slope. It's okay to walk quietly and better at night.
